<bibRefCitation author="Stal" box="[1271,1398,838,863]" pageId="10" pageNumber="446" refString="Stal, C. (1862) Bidrag till Rio Janeiro-Traktens Hemipter-Fauna. Kongliga Svenska Fetenskaps-Akademiens Handlingar, 3, 1 - 70." type="journal article" year="1862">Stål (1862)</bibRefCitation>
